{"tid":995803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過隔咗陣再追返之前鍾意嘅女仔 最後又成功？","createTime":"2019-01-25T17:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T02:54:03.000Z","uid":198680,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef3772c0ac338e8dca35ee6df2060033d8c6a49","tid":995803,"uid":198680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n樓主有個<span style=\"color: red;\">frd</span>ok靚仔 不時都可以吸引到小小女仔approch佢(不過質素多數麻麻) 佢都唔會成日主動撩女仔吹水 <br />\n咁我個frd之後遇到有個女仔對佢有意思(至少係個女仔d frd同我個frd講 除非個女仔d frd玩9人la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )  出頭我個frd同個女仔認識後就日日食dinner/下午茶 我個frd就對個女仔好感慢慢加深 但係我個frd個弱點就係鍾意人就會緊張 所以之後表現到成個on9仔咁 過咗一個月之後就慢慢冇聯絡<br />\n我個frd以為淨係識咗一個月 咁感情都唔會太深厚 點知過咗兩個半月都仲係好掛住個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問有冇人試過追追下女斷咗冇追 之後追返又成功or失敗嘅例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：其實知道情況on9兼複雜 但係我個frd掛住條女 日日催9我開post幫佢問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef031437fcf47d8e60cdbf84b0a38d705c0b51cb","tid":995803,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"931a7ed977393e7b88d7e6e5808662efa9ee58bd","tid":995803,"uid":198680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef031437fcf47d8e60cdbf84b0a38d705c0b51cb","tid":995803,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c80a8790da5dbbd8c7872929a5902b264bb51f","tid":995803,"uid":9,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:52:43.000Z","msg":"我都想試下<br />\n個女仔面對面同埋手機WHATSAPP兩回事"},{"pid":"9c4ceaab8fceadedcf00a5fa9abfd5ea04d57951","tid":995803,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T17:53:14.000Z","msg":"無無無"},{"pid":"dda66c